div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7574eb1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7574eb1\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-20d5b76 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"20d5b76\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Navjivan's Globe Valve<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db11f31 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"db11f31\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Forged Steel Globe Valve<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-519f3d5 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"519f3d5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Forged steel globe valves are essential components in piping systems across various industries. They offer reliable flow control, isolation, and throttling capabilities, making them suitable for high-pressure and high-temperature applications.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Design and Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">\u2022 Forged steel globe valves are typically constructed from high-quality forged steel materials such as ASTM A105, ASTM A182 F11, F22, or stainless steel ASTM A182 F316. This construction provides excellent strength, durability, and resistance to corrosion.<\/span><\/p><p>\u2022 Forged steel globe valves are available with threaded, socket weld, or flanged ends to suit various piping configurations.<\/p><p>\u2022 Bolted bonnet or pressure seal bonnet designs are commonly used to ensure a secure seal even at high pressures.<\/p><p>\u2022 The globe valve&#8217;s plug or disc is designed to press against the seat, providing a tight seal to prevent leakage.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Materials of Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Forged steel globe valves are typically constructed from high-quality forged steel materials such as ASTM A105, ASTM A182 F11, F22, or stainless steel ASTM A182 F316. This construction provides excellent strength, durability, and resistance to corrosion.<\/p><p>\u2022 The disc and seat are designed to provide tight sealing and efficient flow control. They are often made from hardened materials such as stainless steel, Stellite, or other hard-facing alloys to withstand wear and ensure longevity.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Standards and Certifications:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Forged steel globe valves are manufactured in accordance with industry standards such as API 602 or ASME B16.34 for forged steel valves.<\/p><p>\u2022 Material certifications and compliance with other standards (API, ANSI, ISO, etc.) are available upon request.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ee23505 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ee23505\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6750c9a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6750c9a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e14eded e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e14eded\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8c1b2a1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8c1b2a1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" src=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/bolted-globe-valves.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2416\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/bolted-globe-valves.jpg 700w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/bolted-globe-valves-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/bolted-globe-valves-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b13889b e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"b13889b\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d4fb5dd animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d4fb5dd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Navjivan's Globe Valve<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-882e09d animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"882e09d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Bolted Globe Valves<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-29d724e elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"29d724e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Bolted globe valves are a type of industrial valve used to control the flow of liquids or gases through a pipeline. They are named for their globe-like shape, with a spherical body and a movable disk (or plug) that regulates the flow by either being raised or lowered onto the seat, controlling the passage of fluid.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Design and Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Bolted globe valves typically consist of a body, bonnet, disk (or plug), stem, and seating surfaces. The body is usually spherical or cylindrical in shape, with flanged ends for connection to piping systems.<\/p><p>\u2022 The bonnet houses the stem and disk assembly, providing a seal to prevent leakage. The disk is the movable component that regulates flow, while the stem connects the operator (such as a handwheel or actuator) to the disk.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Materials of Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Bolted globe valves are typically made from materials such as carbon steel, stainless steel, cast iron, bronze, or exotic alloys like Hastelloy or Inconel, depending on the specific application requirements including fluid compatibility, temperature, and pressure.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Standards and Certifications:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Globe valves are often manufactured according to industry standards such as API (American Petroleum Institute), ANSI (American National Standards Institute), ASTM (American Society for Testing and Materials), and ASME (American Society of Mechanical Engineers).<\/p><p>\u2022 They may also be certified to meet specific regulatory requirements such as those of the American Society of Mechanical Engineers (ASME) Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e645cf7 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e645cf7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b1433b5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"b1433b5\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a3278fe e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a3278fe\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f45833c elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"f45833c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" src=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/pressure-sealed-globe-valves.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2417\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/pressure-sealed-globe-valves.jpg 700w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/pressure-sealed-globe-valves-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/pressure-sealed-globe-valves-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66eae66 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"66eae66\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a29dc46 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a29dc46\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Navjivan's Globe Valve<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2134d5c animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2134d5c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pressure Sealed Globe Valves<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-890b1a1 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"890b1a1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Pressure-sealed globe valves are a specific type of globe valve designed for high-pressure and high-temperature applications. They feature a unique pressure seal bonnet design that enhances their ability to withstand extreme conditions without leaking.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Design and Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Pressure-sealed globe valves have a robust design featuring a pressure seal bonnet arrangement.<\/p><p>\u2022 Unlike conventional bolted bonnet globe valves, pressure-sealed valves utilize a threaded, welded, or bolted bonnet that forms a pressure-tight seal with the valve body.<\/p><p>\u2022 This design eliminates the need for a gasket, reducing the risk of leaks in high-pressure applications.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Materials of Construction:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Pressure-sealed globe valves are typically constructed from high-quality materials such as carbon steel, stainless steel, alloy steel, or other specialized alloys suitable for high-pressure and high-temperature environments.<\/p><p>\u2022 The choice of materials depends on factors such as the fluid being handled, operating conditions, and corrosion resistance requirements.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Standards and Certifications:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u2022 Pressure Sealed Globe Valves are manufactured in accordance with industry standards and specifications such as API (American Petroleum Institute), ASME (American Society of Mechanical Engineers), ASTM (American Society for Testing and Materials), ANSI (American National Standards Institute), and other relevant standards.<\/p><p>\u2022 They may also undergo testing and certification processes to ensure compliance with regulatory requirements and quality standards.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-37c8f3b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"37c8f3b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-731015c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"731015c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-62b2e44 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"62b2e44\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0b4d7a3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"0b4d7a3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img lo